name: Love by Artifex
description:
“-Is love still love after a person spoils everything? - I ask Destiny between a bite and another of a cake.

-Well, - Fate points to the slice - Carrot cake is your favorite. If I threw vinegar and worms and worms and slugs on it, would carrot cake still be your favorite? - I think a little.

-I think so- I finally answer- I mean, it would still be the best taste.

-But would you eat the cake?

I drop the fork. I understood"
